---

This plugin contains substantive Spanish tax law guidance that is jurisdiction-specific
and time-sensitive. Citations to Spanish primary sources (LIS, LIVA, LIRPF, LGT,
DGT consultas, TEAC resolutions, Tribunal Supremo judgments) and EU/OECD instruments
(Directives, Model Rules, BEPS guidance) reflect the state at the time of writing.
Users are responsible for verifying current status before relying on any guidance
for client work. See `references/resources/tax-currency-watch.md` for the staleness
protocol.

The plugin is provided as a tool to support tax practitioners; it does not replace
professional judgment, and outputs require human verification before use in
client deliverables.
